  "chunk_type": "subsection",
  "content": "Prerequisites: Dex 21, Run.\nBenefit: The character's speed increases by 30 feet. This benefit does not stack with increased speed granted by magic items or nonpermanent magical effects.\nSpecial: This feat only functions when the character is wearing medium armor, light armor, or no armor.",
